lead_paragraph: Leicester City missed the chance to book an early spot in the Champions League's knockout stages as they survived some nervy moments to secure a goalless draw with FC Copenhagen in Group G on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Leicester Made to Wait After Goalless Draw in Copenhagen
